groups.label: • Avoiding your need to travel to the specialist
• Assisting your local health service to better look after you
• A video consultation will not be exactly the same, and may not be as complete as a face-to-face service.
• There could be some technical problems that could affect the consultation
• We cannot guarantee total protection against hacking or tapping into the video visit by outsiders. This risk is small, but it does exist.
I can change my mind and stop using video consultations at any time, including in the middle of a telehealth consult. This will not make any difference to my right to ask for and receive health care.

I understand it may be necessary to have videos recorded or photographs taken if required. This will be saved securely and only be used to benefit my healthcare. I have the right to see the video or images if desired.
